      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Attention: Chief, Counterintelligence Division",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "From: John Edgar Hoover, Director",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Subject: UNIDENTIFIED FLYING OBJECT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "SEPTEMBER 22, 1961, IN VICINITY",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "OF WASHINGTON, D. C.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "On September 22, 1961, [REDACTED] advised this Bureau",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "that between 2:00 a.m. and 2:25 a.m. on September 22, 1961, he",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "had observed a light which he felt could be a flying disc. He",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "explained that the light which was in the East seemed to change",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "colors and to ascend and descend. He discounted the possibility",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "that the light was from an aircraft or was a falling star.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "The above information was furnished to Captain [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "Department of the Air Force, at 2:30 a.m. September 22,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "1961, by Special Agent [REDACTED] of this Bureau. We are",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "taking no further action with respect to this matter.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
